tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE training_sessions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_date DATE,
    duration_minutes INT,
    neural_network_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (neural_network_id) REFERENCES neural_networks(id)
);

CREATE TABLE training_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    neural_network_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    input_values VARCHAR(255),
    output_values VARCHAR(255),
    FOREIGN KEY (neural_network_id) REFERENCES neural_networks(id)
);
